@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About</PageTitle>

<h1>About EventEase</h1>
<p>
    EventEase is a simple event management system built with Blazor and .NET 10.
    It demonstrates reusable components, routing, form validation, responsive UI, and in-memory state management.
</p>
<p>
    This project is designed to be easy to read and beginner-friendly, so each page focuses on one clear task.
</p>
